CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A4, reads: "Hat Model - ...Delta Sigma Theta's fashion show at the William Penn Hotel recently, when she modeled a number of custom made hats created by Ruth Lee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of woman modeling satin dress, light colored hat, and holding fur stole, posed near mural of West End - North Side Bridge, Pittsburgh, for Delta Sigma Theta fashion show, William Penn Hotel
